reviewText:
DO NOT PURCHASE! This DVD does not have the entire season! Nowhere does the description show that it has only 17 episodes... My daughter loves this show and was really upset that she did not have the full season.
An honest company would clearly show that this is not a full season, while this one simply did not mention it!
There are less than 1/2 of the episodes from this season on this DVD. No where does it state that it's only a partial season.
